{"tid":1428002,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺近呢幾個月支那果三大發展計劃已經無乜聲氣","createTime":"2019-08-07T08:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:35:25.000Z","uid":122604,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"69749581cdd48db1295fc22fd59089a9bdf714ad","tid":1428002,"uid":122604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"話哂支那係發展中國家, 發展速度緊係都要成為最大贏家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過隨意係網上搵下新聞, 發覺呢排除左搵人亮劍同護旗之外對外經濟發展好似停滯哂<br />\n有乜錯漏等各巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>亞投行</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/business/benin-rwanda-and-djibouti-to-join-asian-infrastructure-investment-bank/articleshow/70206299.cms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2Fbusiness%2Fbenin-rwanda-and-djibouti-to-join-asian-infrastructure-investment-bank%2Farticleshow%2F70206299.cms&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=283f77f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/business/benin-rwanda-and-djibouti-to-join-asian-infrastructure-investment-bank/articleshow/70206299.cms</a><br />\n嘩好勁原來已經有100個成員, 但原來新加入果3個係窮鬼非洲國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>大灣區</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/360284/%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%8C-%E7%BA%8C%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E4%BA%92%E8%81%AF%E4%BA%92%E9%80%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F360284%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E7%25BA%258C%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E4%25BA%2592%25E8%2581%25AF%25E4%25BA%2592%25E9%2580%259A&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=01c589a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/360284/%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%8C-%E7%BA%8C%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E4%BA%92%E8%81%AF%E4%BA%92%E9%80%9A</a><br />\n金融市場互聯互通&hellip;即係方便支那吸走香港資金應付貿易戰<br />\n除左呢樣之外就得番啲呃人買爛尾樓既廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>一帶一路</ins><br />\n我都想搵外媒新聞歌頌下, 話哂都係大project要揚威國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知除左馬來西亞鐵路復工之外都係得啲吹水野, 算啦有得開工都當贏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be6aecafce1cadd96193ed13fad3f8d2a6d614b","tid":1428002,"uid":122604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:35:25.000Z","msg":"當然唔少得支那好引以自豪既西部大開發<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/西部大開發\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%A5%BF%E9%83%A8%E5%A4%A7%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=124874f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/西部大開發</a> <br />\n<br />\n點知碌到去最底&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OP4X0ez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOP4X0ez.png&h=a0413221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來連條link都死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}